{"tid":160612,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"林太請「專家食屎」 嘉湖樓價一年勁升30%","createTime":"2017-03-17T23:30:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-18T11:19:47.000Z","uid":17738,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f57bc24609b8291c0767cbf5c042c0d042142478","tid":160612,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T23:30:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/18/073032_fb1569c8296e5e96bba0d0953d58a51c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F18%2F073032_fb1569c8296e5e96bba0d0953d58a51c.jpg&h=1dabdf12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去年1月6日，蘋果記者直擊天水圍嘉湖山莊，當時區內業主林太表示，半個月前阿仔買入樂湖居兩房單位，成交價330萬元。被問到市場不少專家指樓價跌一成，林太豪氣回應，「290萬已經最低，我個仔買貴40萬冇咩問題，佢要住㗎嘛，如果升又點呢。阿仔買嘅單位，銀行估到價，銀行唔會死錯人嘅，嗰啲咁既專家，食屎啦！我哋唔係有見地，我哋係腳踏實地，唔聽專家㗎，聽專家意見就死啦。」<br />\n<br />\n林太發表「專家食屎」論當日，嘉湖山莊的平均呎價只是約6,800元，兩房單位300萬元有交易，但在14個月後的今日，由於剛錄得一宗兩房連天台單位成交，嘉湖山莊本月的平均呎價被拉高至近9,000元，樓價升幅逾三成。<br />\n<br />\n事實勝於雄辯，的而且確，如果當日信專家樓價仲有得跌，而沒有入市，錯過低位入市機會，學林太話齋，「嗰啲咁既專家，食屎啦」。今日，林太已成為網民心目中的樓市英雄，更勝樓市專家。<br />\n<br />\n另外，不少網民八卦林太兒子一年半前買入兩房單位今日價值，根據她當日提供資料，記者查到他兒子單位，目前中銀及滙豐估價分別為405萬元及400萬元，以當日買入價330萬元計，單位升值22.7%及21.2%。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/financeestate/art/20170308/19950864\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Ffinanceestate%2Fart%2F20170308%2F19950864&d=Rx4KuutU7IQQNt32%2FBGh6viMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=855e04da\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Ffinanceestate%2Fart%2F20170308%2F19950864&h=048a3718\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/financeestate/art/20170308/19950864</a>"},{"pid":"d9ab2987e1bae091140c023beb36fdde10e52755","tid":160612,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T23:37:19.000Z","msg":"2016年1月，又再證明做生意又好，買樓都好，信高登仔一成都死得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當時幾多「高登樓市磚家」笑鳩人c9唔識，千套理論下跌多幾多成 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e1a158ec38ffe9a4f4cca7cf7e8e74f47b68cac","tid":160612,"uid":63212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T00:01:44.000Z","msg":"330, 宜家440?"},{"pid":"253cb41e992c0ef9f75abb675c65fcf1a4b5b3c6","tid":160612,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T00:08:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>330, 宜家440?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n430-440冇乜走雞，如果以一成33萬加上其他費用，45萬夠，1年贏1球，乜都冇做過<br />\n<br />\n每個論壇講樓市就有股神出現，比45萬任你炒乜都好1年贏到1球?"},{"pid":"3ff75d5dc141e10e7427854a988e8f910e68016d","tid":160612,"uid":24177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T00:10:27.000Z","msg":"有霸氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd3065ca667cac477064cc86f6ee7ed6d364f12f","tid":160612,"uid":73241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T00:12:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e74ce4e8e520a61b569c33b4e615005a29e15f7","tid":160612,"uid":66769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T00:17:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>330, 宜家440?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n430-440冇乜走雞，如果以一成33萬加上其他費用，45萬夠，1年贏1球，乜都冇做過<br />\n<br />\n每個論壇講樓市就有股神出現，比45萬任你炒乜都好1年贏到1球?</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64ca50ac9904fd5686558b8e37b98157618cad39","tid":160612,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T00:21:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>330, 宜家440?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n430-440冇乜走雞，如果以一成33萬加上其他費用，45萬夠，1年贏1球，乜都冇做過<br />\n<br />\