5萬任你炒乜都好1年贏到1球?</blockquote><br />\n我以前係證券行做account &amp; settlement可以睇晒客戶資料，10炒股9個輸這話是真的<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc740f7a37db811cc7971cd8a7ade00ecb5d814a","tid":160612,"uid":45290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T00:46:44.000Z","msg":"林太哩句永遠都直擊連登仔要害"},{"pid":"5aab71e5cd50a3057533436a5b3ae7cae7e75e76","tid":160612,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T00:50:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>330, 宜家440?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n430-440冇乜走雞，如果以一成33萬加上其他費用，45萬夠，1年贏1球，乜都冇做過<br />\n<br />\n每個論壇講樓市就有股神出現，比45萬任你炒乜都好1年贏到1球?</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又係喎 330萬做一成首期<br />\n<br />\n45萬連雜費<br />\n<br />\n45萬 年半升左100萬<br />\n<br />\n返左兩倍</blockquote><br />\n還埋利息賺幾多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n嘉湖11000租，供嘅錢可以自己計，網上大把，供落去有本金嘅，平過租，銀行提供十倍槓桿，去證券行擺低45萬，點借十倍孖展比你，炒期指有槓桿，1年賺到1球我真係唔知有幾多個?"},{"pid":"94e0a4226173508cd8e22b56be122d34165a40c9","tid":160612,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T01:01:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>330, 宜家440?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n430-440冇乜走雞，如果以一成33萬加上其他費用，45萬夠，1年贏1球，乜都冇做過<br />\n<br />\n每個論壇講樓市就有股神出現，比45萬任你炒乜都好1年贏到1球?</blockquote><br />\n我以前係證券行做account &amp; settlement可以睇晒客戶資料，10炒股9個輸這話是真的<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都炒股，如果2016年有個高登仔揸住45萬，擺去炒股1年可能輸一半，跟林太尾依家唔使叫春，執一球，唔係點解我話得一注錢買樓先，除咗解決住嘅問題先，香港長期計磚頭輸極有譜，再升加按1開二，跌就住，當交租"},{"pid":"6ebef719f948cf944958c8f7d9019afcfdcbc316","tid":160612,"uid":46947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T01:22:40.000Z","msg":"係咪即係叫屍永青食屎？"},{"pid":"e718a9041e2fbf73e9813b86f14be1e2a7310889","tid":160612,"uid":75196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T01:25:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪即係叫屍永青食屎？</blockquote><br />\n你見佢而家都轉軚就知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5403fa28162e250de34a3a707d3dff7caa47de4b","tid":160612,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T01:26:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪即係叫屍永青食屎？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔止，仲有風水佬蘇文峰，磚家湯文亮，經濟學者關焯照教授，一眾高登樓市磚家，林太邊度痾得切比佢哋食? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ce45a94a785a8cd8e84b53106648551aff01dde","tid":160612,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T01:33:39.000Z","msg":"樓市Gogogog<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e2a4f47d47fccc4a00d304b6e949bd420175807","tid":160612,"uid":6677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T01:43:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係咪即係叫屍永青食屎？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔止，仲有風水佬蘇文峰，磚家湯文亮，經濟學者關焯照教授，一眾高登樓市磚家，林太邊度痾得切比佢哋食? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n高燈仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d1eb3dcd5e5bc3ae30b826f0d9bc42887ae23ff","tid":160612,"uid":35315,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T01:47:57.000Z","msg":"香港啲樓好難輸錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算再多一次沙士都唔會跌得幾多，03年個時班人真係執到"},{"pid":"8b1e2fd055af1aef97758211aee358046e1d37f1","tid":160612,"uid":37723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T01:51:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係咪即係叫屍永青食屎？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔止，仲有風水佬蘇文峰，磚家湯文亮，經濟學者關焯照教授，一